title: Green Bay Packers 2014 Complete Season (Condensed)
description:
Green Bay Packers Entire 2014 Season (Pre-Season, Regular, Playoffs).

All games are condensed, which means there's no commercials. It goes from play-to-play-to-play. Making each game about 45 minutes long or so.

Most of these games are HDTV rips, and a few are WEBrips from NFL Game Rewind.

All games are in either 1080p or 720.    
    
Enjoy! And look for some other releases, as I plan on doing the entire NFC North!
